header.description:
Gametest Framework Wrapper is a library built using Minecraft Bedrock Edition Gametest Framework API.
This library will help you keep your code clean and make it easier to interact with the Gametest Framework API, while including a lot of new functions for you to use!
This pack will have some miscellaneous and some custom command that you may use!
